    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to Gradation 1 and not assessed per MRL 2 requirements. Discretization error exceeds requirement (Gradation 3 achieved vs. 2 required). Output comparison confirms NIH predictions within 11.3% of experimental measurements across all 5 COU operating points. RH < 1 criterion met for all worst-case operating conditions. Credibility sufficient to support regulatory submission for Class II CPB device.",
